{"id":296366,"magazine_id":26272,"template_id":41,"title":"Een dag bij - tester","alias":"een-dag-bij-tester","page_no":8,"meta_keywords":null,"meta_description":null,"share_url":null,"options":{"has_disabled_header":false,"exclude_from_navigationbar":false,"share_url":null},"header":null,"content":{"background":{"filename":"achtergrond-melchior.796c3815ead6.jpg","uri":"\/images\/achtergrond-melchior.796c3815ead6.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":184331,"width":1600,"height":925},"nav_type":"bars","sidebar":1,"image":{"filename":"melchior2_gebouw.01820e686574.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior2_gebouw.01820e686574.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":695355,"width":1600,"height":1067},"title":"EEN DAG BIJ","subtitle":"Christophorus groep Melchior","description":"<p><br><\/p><p>De jongeren van Melchior heten ons van harte welkom in hun nieuwe woning. Sinds eind 2016 wonen ze met drie andere groepen in de nieuwbouw aan de Duinweg in Bosch en Duin. In februari was de feestelijke opening. Ze laten ons zien hoe hun dag eruit ziet vanaf het moment dat ze thuiskomen rond theetijd tot ze naar bed gaan.&nbsp;<\/p>","text_align":"left","header_space":"0","item":[{"title":null,"subtitle":null,"description":null,"item":[{"image":{"filename":"melchior3-lara_en_elisa.4818d8036c1e.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior3-lara_en_elisa.4818d8036c1e.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":450315,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Begeleider Elisa komt om Lara uit de bus te halen. Weer thuis!<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior3-lara.9d609ca4bd9a.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior3-lara.9d609ca4bd9a.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":402068,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Lara heet ons van harte welkom in haar nieuwe huis.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior3_kiezen.d1d34acea0dd.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior3_kiezen.d1d34acea0dd.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":293164,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Kies je fruit. Even bijkomen na een lange dag.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"muziek_therapie.2ef3970401a9.jpg","uri":"\/images\/muziek_therapie.2ef3970401a9.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":351838,"width":1600,"height":1134},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Lotte krijgt een keer per week muziektherapie.&nbsp;<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior-spelen.67c2cd679467.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior-spelen.67c2cd679467.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":418167,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Buiten spelen! Op 13 mei is er een sponsordag om geld in te zamelen om deze kale tuin op te knappen.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior2-178.fa29ba29420d.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior2-178.fa29ba29420d.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":397142,"width":1600,"height":1096},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Tijd om&nbsp;voor te lezen<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior_ritueel.fedc0a7c5896.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior_ritueel.fedc0a7c5896.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":419758,"width":1600,"height":1136},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Melchior is een antroposofische groep.&nbsp;In de kring elkaar de hand geven is een van de vaste rituelen.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior-eten.7ea597679c6c.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior-eten.7ea597679c6c.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":346665,"width":1600,"height":1078},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Lotte en haar moeder staan nog even in de keuken. Een keer in de week eet haar moeder mee.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior_naar_bed.5fa9f64180a6.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior_naar_bed.5fa9f64180a6.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":453620,"width":1600,"height":955},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>Pyjama aan. Tijd om&nbsp;naar bed te gaan.<\/p>"},{"image":{"filename":"melchior2-439.0978727b33b3.jpg","uri":"\/images\/melchior2-439.0978727b33b3.jpg","alt":null,"filemime":"image\/jpeg","filesize":396316,"width":1600,"height":1067},"youtube":null,"alt_image":null,"description":"<p>De avond is gevallen. Slaap lekker!<\/p>"}],"style":{"title":["color: ;","color: ;"],"subtitle":["color: ;","color: ;"],"paragraph":["color: ;","color: ;"]}}],"padding":null}}